            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>泓瀚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4741:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4741\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4741-TW</a>)26日09:34上漲2.7元，股價漲停報30.1元，委買521,000張，成交1,595張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為噴墨印刷、廣告設備及墨水生產。Micro LED, 半導體零配件,細胞染色,病毒檢測等噴墨製程代工。電子材料及特用化學品奈米化製造。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>泓瀚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4741:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4741\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4741-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌7.42%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌5.06%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-36 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-40 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+4 張</li> <li>融資增減：+178 張</li> <li>融券增減：-1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
